data.description: Experience the future in Denton, TX with Sandlin Homes' new construction at Eagle Cove. Only a few miles from TWU & UNT, this luxurious property is perfect for investors, students & families. Both sides of a modern duplex unit are included in this listing, each featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 luxurious bathrooms, & 1.5-car garage per side. Estimated completion for the first 8 units is July 2024, making it a prime real estate opportunity. The homes come loaded with various upscale features. In the kitchen, you'll find a sleek island w elegant granite countertops & top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Units are equipped w keyless entry & security system. The master bath is equipped w a relaxing garden tub & walk-in closets. Energy efficiency & long-term savings ensured w Low-E glass vinyl windows. Sandlin Homes takes your peace of mind seriously, offering a StrucSure 10 Year home warranty to protect your investment. *4 bedroom units also available. Call us today to secure yours!
